    <div class="col-md-7"><h4>Why its works</h4>
    <p>The firefly device have a unique ability to accelerate athlete’s recovery after exercise and minor injury within 24 hours. This increase in blood flow accelerates recovery from high intensity exercise and promotes healing after injury.  Blood transport the nutrients required to rebuild the body tissues and help to expel metabolic waste from tissue. The firefly device helps muscles recover quickly by increasing blood flow to reduce muscle soreness after intense exercise, assisting athletes to get back to training faster and improve performance. . Using firefly to increase blood flow to the injured area in lower limbs to reduces swelling and aids in the recovery from sprains and strains. . We do recommend that you seek advice from your doctor or physiotherapist before using firefly to treat an injury. </p>
