    <h4>Reducing the Risk of Injury</h4>
    <p>An injury caused by sudden impact is hard to avoid whereas fatigue and overuse injuries are very common, especially in professional athletes because of the intense nature of training. All injuries cannot avoided there are the ways to reduce the risk of injury these including following as:</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Managing fatigue effectively.</li>
      <li>Adequate rest and recovery.</li>
      <li>Warming up properly before exercise.</li>
      <li>Performing an active recovery after exercise.</li>
    </ol>
